{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.200", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.440", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.840", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.040", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es stimmt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.360", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bakterien kommen \u00fcberall vor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.400", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und das ist erst mal gut so. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.200", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen Bakterien auf unserer Haut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.520", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in unserem Darm, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.840", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Boden und auch \u00fcberall sonst in der Umwelt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.440", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.560", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist auch richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.960", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass gerade im Wasser sehr h\u00e4ufig sehr resistente Keime vorkommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.920", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist erst mal kein Grund zur Sorge."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.480", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber was wir jetzt finden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.480", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist etwas v\u00f6llig anderes. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.920", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Seen und B\u00e4chen wurden Keime in relevanter Zahl gefunden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.000", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auch beim Menschen vorkommen und die gerade gegen sehr wichtige Antibiotika resistent sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.880", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das kommt nicht von ungef\u00e4hr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.320", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach dem Motto \u201eViel hilft viel\u201c wurden in der Behandlung von Menschen zu h\u00e4ufig und teilweise falsch dosiert Antibiotika eingesetzt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.680", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber noch viel mehr\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.280", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das muss man bedenken\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.240", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wurden und werden sie in der Tierhaltung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.240", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich tonnenweise, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.600", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verwendet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.880", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mittlerweile gibt es Einschr\u00e4nkungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.360", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "doch das reicht l\u00e4ngst nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.520", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es haben sich Resistenzen herausgebildet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.520", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese werden zwischen den Bakterien weitergegeben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.280", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und letztendlich erreichen sie \u00fcber Umwege auch uns Menschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.240", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und das ist dramatisch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.080", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn immerhin sterben jedes Jahr weltweit \u00fcber 700\u00a0000\u00a0Menschen an Infektionen durch multiresistente Bakterien. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.840", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das d\u00fcrfen wir einfach nicht hinnehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.080", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bakterielle Erkrankungen waren eine Gei\u00dfel der Menschheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.320", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bis die Wirkung der Antibiotika entdeckt wurde und sie f\u00fcr alle Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.640", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zumindest hier bei uns, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.240", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zur Verf\u00fcgung standen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.040", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist noch nicht lange her. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.520", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fragen Sie mal nach, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.400", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie viele Kinder und Erwachsene an Diphtherie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.720", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "entz\u00fcndeten Wunden oder sogar an einem l\u00e4cherlichen vereiterten Zahn gestorben sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.200", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe zehn Jahre lang in der Diagnostik bakterieller Erkrankungen gearbeitet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.120", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich wei\u00df, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.920", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie schwer und vor allen Dingen wie schnell ein Krankheitsverlauf ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.800", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn nicht das geeignete Medikament gefunden wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.080", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage Ihnen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.960", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wollen wir alle nicht haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.800", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist nicht lustig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.320", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie solche Keime nach einer ganz einfachen OP pl\u00f6tzlich im Knie haben oder wenn sie auf Ihrer Herzklappe sitzen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.440", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da sitzen sie n\u00e4mlich sehr gerne. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.600", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn genau diese Keime heutzutage in Badegew\u00e4ssern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.400", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in unseren B\u00e4chen und Fl\u00fcssen gefunden werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.560", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann ist das keine abstrakte Gefahr mehr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.720", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Hessen ist zum Beispiel ein Mann gestorben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.400", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der in einen Bach gefallen ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.760", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er ist nicht ertrunken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.160", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er ist an einer Infektion mit Bakterien gestorben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.680", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die nachweislich aus diesem Bach stammten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.440", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit dieses Schicksal nicht weitere Menschen trifft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.160", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen wir jetzt handeln."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.720", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum einen brauchen wir einen \u00dcberblick. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.760", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht die Presse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.320", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern unsere Beh\u00f6rden m\u00fcssen das Wasser untersuchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.160", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "M\u00f6glichkeiten sind da. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.480", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allein in Hessen gibt es \u00fcber 200\u00a0Messstellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.320", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man muss nur weitere Parameter untersuchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.640", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist machbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.920", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist bezahlbar."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.640", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum anderen m\u00fcssen wir den Umgang mit Medikamenten \u00fcberdenken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.480", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ganz grunds\u00e4tzlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.840", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und bei der Herstellung mehr Wert auf Umweltvertr\u00e4glichkeit legen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.360", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf gezielte Verschreibungen achten und bei der Entsorgung aufpassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.840", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass R\u00fcckst\u00e4nde und Keime nicht ins Wasser gelangen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.560", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor allen Dingen muss Schluss sein mit dem Einsatz von Reserveantibiotika, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.400", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel Colistin. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.600", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wird beim Menschen nur verwendet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.200", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn nichts anderes mehr hilft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.360", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Gefl\u00fcgelstall geh\u00f6rt das noch zum Standardprogramm."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.800", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das alles schlagen wir in unserem Antrag vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.000", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Gesundheit der B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger zu sch\u00fctzen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.520", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn Wasser ist Lebenselixier, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.320", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das muss es bleiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.800", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar um jeden Preis."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.840", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.920", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.800", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin Dr.\u00a0Hoffmann.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.480", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als N\u00e4chster erteile ich das Wort meiner schleswig-holsteinischen Kollegin Astrid Damerow f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "284.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.200", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich darf darauf hinweisen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.960", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch f\u00fcr sie ist es die erste Parlamentsrede im Deutschen Bundestag."
   ]
  }
 ]
}